Subject: [PATCH] hibyr1: register milkdrop visualiser plugin

Add the milkdrop Milkdrop-style feedback visualiser (overlay/apps/plugins/
milkdrop.c) to the plugin build and the demos category.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 apps/plugins/CATEGORIES | 1 +
 apps/plugins/SOURCES    | 1 +
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/apps/plugins/CATEGORIES b/apps/plugins/CATEGORIES
index bf646a5bf9..ef53a82f83 100644
--- a/apps/plugins/CATEGORIES
+++ b/apps/plugins/CATEGORIES
@@ -79,6 +79,7 @@ mpegplayer,viewers
 multiboot_select,apps
 nim,games
 open_plugins,viewers
+milkdrop,demos
 oscilloscope,demos
 otp,apps
 pacbox,games
diff --git a/apps/plugins/SOURCES b/apps/plugins/SOURCES
index 797601e4dd..6445ab2750 100644
--- a/apps/plugins/SOURCES
+++ b/apps/plugins/SOURCES
@@ -151,6 +151,7 @@ demystify.c
 jewels.c
 minesweeper.c
 open_plugins.c
+milkdrop.c
 oscilloscope.c
 pegbox.c
 periodic_table.c
